IMAPStore mailbox-remote
Host imap.mailbox.org
UserCmd "pass show www/mail/mailbox.org/username"
PassCmd "pass show www/mail/mailbox.org/password"
TLSType IMAPS

MaildirStore mailbox-local
Path  ~/.mail/mailbox/
Inbox ~/.mail/mailbox/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel mailbox
Far :mailbox-remote:
Near :mailbox-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All

IMAPStore disroot-remote
Host disroot.org
UserCmd "pass show www/mail/disroot.org/email"
PassCmd "pass show www/mail/disroot.org/password"
TLSType IMAPS

MaildirStore disroot-local
Path  ~/.mail/disroot/
Inbox ~/.mail/disroot/INBOX
SubFolders Verbatim

Channel disroot
Far :disroot-remote:
Near :disroot-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Sync All
